summary:
A driven self-starter with experience in multiple functions across the payments organisation with a focus on business development, account management and partnerships.

In my free time, I am the founder and artist at SYNT Studio, a design studio specialising in game design, artwork and branding, and creator of popular Singaporean local card games such as The Singaporean Dream and Hawker Wars. See our work at www.synt.studio

Adaptable and resilient, with a breadth of global exposure - looking for opportunities to grow professionally, stretch leadership capabilities and make a meaningful impact on the world.
